metadata.name: Shrooms Capsule
metadata.description:
To get the Freaky Trippy Allen, you should burn 3 grams of these mushrooms. Each edition of shrooms capsule equals 1 gram of mushroom.

After you took a capsule, read this description, otherwise you’d be confused cause it is not understandable to a third dimensional mind!

BE AWARE:  
Mushrooms will show you the real world!  
Don’t take the risk if you can’t handle the truth!

Angelicat loves challenging you.

High Moses doesn’t like to talk that much.

Weenie alien has firefull thoughts.

Alan is upset about his hair color.

Oscar loves jazz, yet he is a Disc Jogger.

A single eye means three eyes.

Compass is useless if you can’t move fast.
